{"tid":1541580,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"喂屌你老母呢場仗未撚打完 勇武和理非都唔停得","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T08:47:08.000Z","uid":198822,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc00075af453721a7bc55be8fd54dc3bebd4d16","tid":1541580,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2dtQRBi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2dtQRBi.png&h=7f35a94c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊條撚樣政棍po啲咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔對得住今晚先跳咗嘅義士<br />\n五大訴求呀屌你老母 五個呢家都未實現到呀<br />\n你同我講下一仗？<br />\n你同我講叫勇武休息？<br />\n勇武有得休息衝去休息啦？使你提？<br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力 你憑咩叫人地唔勇武？<br />\n呢三個月冇勇武會行到咁遠？狡兔都未撚殺哂你就收埋把良弓？<br />\n知唔知一停會點呀屌你老母 大搜捕 集中營 終極清算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一停就冇架啦 前線要送頭係因為要用自己條命喚起香港人嘅金魚記憶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9ae6e523538f14d6ee777f06242b6f9e4819fb","tid":1541580,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26770b2c377a5e5713c7525f7294fb21da5f2ecb","tid":1541580,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 呢家邊個講選舉邊撚個係鬼呀"},{"pid":"d90f19db061da78b914501cca039d73845076c68","tid":1541580,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5sR8Hg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2